  "safetyCenterTitle": "Safety center",
  "safetyCenterIntro": "A few simple rules to keep exchanges on ShelfShare pleasant and safe.",
  "safetyTip1Title": "Meet during the day",
  "safetyTip1Desc": "Schedule the exchange for a time with natural daylight, ideally morning or afternoon.",
  "safetyTip2Title": "Choose a public place",
  "safetyTip2Desc": "A café, bookstore, or mall is safer than someone's personal address.",
  "safetyTip3Title": "Prefer locations with video surveillance",
  "safetyTip3Desc": "Areas with security cameras discourage unpleasant behavior.",
  "safetyTip4Title": "Don't share personal data",
  "safetyTip4Desc": "You don't need to give your home address, ID number, or other sensitive data to make an exchange.",
  "safetyTip5Title": "Check the rating and trust score",
  "safetyTip5Desc": "A good history of completed exchanges is a good sign before meeting someone.",
  "safetyTip6Title": "A real profile photo builds trust",
  "safetyTip6Desc": "Profiles with a photo and a complete bio inspire more confidence in other users.",
  "safetyTip7Title": "Check the book's condition before the exchange",
  "safetyTip7Desc": "Compare the book to the listing's description before confirming the exchange as completed.",
  "safetyTip8Title": "Report any suspicious behavior",
